      "comment": "Manners let THE DARK THUNDER (8) down last start but he had been flying prior, winning his first three starts off a spell including the Boort and Wangaratta cups. Draws for a trail and with his A-game could return to the winners' list. KYVALLEY JETSTREAM NZ (2) has put together a string of top-three finishes, drawing wide and working when winning here two back and missing by a head last start at Geelong. Draws well and strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit. Tricky draw for SIX NATIONS (12) but he owns good statistics both here and at the distance and could be ready to peak third up. CLAUDYS HERO (9) led to win at Bendigo two back before a second from this barrier here last week. Go well again.",
